      • SUBMISSION

        public static final TimedSchedulerMeterDocumentation.SubmittedTags SUBMISSION
        The type of submission:
        • "direct" for Scheduler.schedule(Runnable)
        • "delayed" for Scheduler.schedule(Runnable, long, TimeUnit)
        • "periodic_initial" for Scheduler.schedulePeriodically(Runnable, long, long, TimeUnit) after the initial delay
        • "periodic_iteration" for Scheduler.schedulePeriodically(Runnable, long, long, TimeUnit) further periodic iterations

    • 字段详细资料

      • SUBMISSION_DIRECT

        public static final java.lang.String SUBMISSION_DIRECT
        Counter that increments by one each time a task is submitted for immediate execution (ie. Scheduler#schedule(Runnable) or Scheduler.Worker#schedule(Runnable)).
        另请参阅:
        常量字段值

      • SUBMISSION_DELAYED

        public static final java.lang.String SUBMISSION_DELAYED
        Counter that increments by one each time a task is submitted with a delay (ie. Scheduler#schedule(Runnable, long, TimeUnit) or Scheduler.Worker#schedule(Runnable, long, TimeUnit)).
        另请参阅:
        常量字段值

      • SUBMISSION_PERIODIC_INITIAL

        public static final java.lang.String SUBMISSION_PERIODIC_INITIAL
        Counter that increments when a task is initially submitted with a period (ie. Scheduler#schedulePeriodically(Runnable, long, long, TimeUnit) or Scheduler.Worker#schedulePeriodically(Runnable, long, long, TimeUnit)). This isn't incremented on further iterations of the periodic task.
        另请参阅:
        常量字段值

      • SUBMISSION_PERIODIC_ITERATION

        public static final java.lang.String SUBMISSION_PERIODIC_ITERATION
        Counter that increments by one each time a task is re-executed due to the periodic nature of Scheduler#schedulePeriodically(Runnable, long, long, TimeUnit) or Scheduler.Worker#schedulePeriodically(Runnable, long, long, TimeUnit) (ie. iterations past the initial one).
        另请参阅:
        常量字段值
